headline: Is Goldman Sachs Still a Smart Pick After 34% Rally and Major Expansion News in 2025?
summary: Ever wondered if Goldman Sachs Group stock is a smart buy at today's price? Let's cut through the noise and focus on what really drives value. The stock has run up 270.5% over five years, with a 31.0% gain in the last year and more than 34% year-to-date. However, it did dip 2.1% in the past week. Much of this momentum is linked to optimism in financial sector innovation and Goldman Sachs Group's role in recent major deals and capital raising activities. These developments have sparked...
